   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3170_0070"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168934">IX. Frankga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 1</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="left"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3170_0069"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>, <date when="1900-09-22">22. September</date>.</dateline></opener><p><salute><anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02933-1"/>M. l. F.<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02933-1">Mein lieber Freund</note>,</salute> die aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs> datirte <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02933-2"/><rs type="work" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb141819">Mittheilung</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02933-2">»<quote>– Aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168"><hi rend="spaced-out">Berlin</hi></rs> wird uns gemeldet: ›<rs type="work" ref="#pmb29857">Der Schleier der
                        Beatrice</rs>‹ von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Arthur <hi rend="spaced-out">Schnitzler</hi></rs> wird im Einvernehmen mit dem <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2121">Dichter</rs> demnächst im <rs type="org" ref="#pmb62965">Breslauer Stadttheater</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eine Er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>taufführung erleben.</quote>«
                     <bibl>[O. V.]: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb141819">Theater- und
                        Kunstnachrichten</rs>. In: <rs type="work" ref="#pmb36374">Neue Freie
                        Presse</rs>, Nr. 12.959, <date when="1900-09-21">21. 9. 1900</date>,
                     Morgenblatt, S. 6–7, hier: S. 7</bibl>.</note> von der Aufführung der »<hi rend="latintype"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb29857">Beatrice</rs></hi>« in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb677">Breslau</rs>, welche <date when="1900-09-21">ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern</date> im Theatertheil der <rs type="work" ref="#pmb36374">N. Fr.
                  Pr.</rs> zu le<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en war,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tammt<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>elb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tver<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tändlich nicht von mir.</p><closer>Viele Grüße! <lb/><signed>P. G.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
